 Icala lihlehliselwe kuMeyi 18, 2022 ukuze kuqhubeke uphenyo. Lokhu kwenzeka ngemva kwesigameko sango-Ephreli  26, esenzeke emfuleni iMogol, osepulazini. Kuthiwa uPaul Hendrick Stephanes Van Zyl (77), wazama ukubulala uRamokone Linah ngenhloso ngesikhathi emdubula. ULinah wayenesoka lakhe emfuleni bedoba ngesikhathi bezwa kuqhuma isibhamu. “ULinah wadubuleka engalweni yakwesokunxele walimala,” kusho uMashudu Malabi-Dzhangi okhulumela abeNPA. Kuthiwa isoka lakwazi ukucasha kanti esebuzwa umsolwa, wathi wayecabanga ukuthi yizimvubu.  